responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "906BD9CE4074B5241613148F0422FBF8", "Ah, so Second Sword send you, Godling. Their eyes, they grow upon Ashen Flame, yes? They seek future in trade, in alliance, but we... we seek peace. Their watchful gaze, it bring promise, but also pressure. But the path I walk, it not for politics alone. It is for people, for land, for spirits.")
